<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id78d4f585-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s939c"><num value="939c">§ 939c.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is hereby authorized to be appropriated from time to time such sums as may be necessary for carrying out the purposes and provisions of the Convention and this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id78d4f586-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-06-04/ch358/s13">June 4, 1956, ch. 358, § 13</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70/244">70 Stat. 244</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
